                <li>Create and add quotations</li>
                <li>Save your favorite quotations</li>
                <li>Create custom books</li>
                <li>Create custom authors</li>
                <li>Store public or private quotations</li>
                <li>Save your favorite books</li>
                <li>Save your favorite authors</li>
            </ul>
